🎯 Project: Student Grade Calculator
Build a program that takes student marks and returns grade (A, B, C, etc.) with encouraging messages

    🛠️ Technical Requirements:
    Use if-elif-else statements for grading logic
    Add input validation (marks 0-100 only)
    Create at least one function
    Add encouraging messages for each grade
    Use while loop to handle invalid inputs

    📋 Step-by-Step Guide:
    Day 1: Understand Grading System - Create grade rules document
    Day 2: Create Input System - Get student name and marks
    Day 3: Add Grading Logic - Implement if-elif-else conditions
    Day 4: Add Validation & Loop - Check marks range, handle invalid inputs
    Day 5: Create Final Program - Combine all parts, add functions, test thoroughly
